{"tid":1215235,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】【國際頭條】將黑警打人相、片加返多國語言Caption／字幕","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T08:34:23.000Z","uid":212671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3dea6724edab4aedc0141c5a31a8e3f59ecb6125","tid":1215235,"uid":212671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:30:24.000Z","msg":"文宣小組真心無咁勇，但都想盡返小小綿力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望每日都有啲有代表性嘅 image，令到件事持續不斷有外媒報導，上到比較前嘅版面，起碼去到20號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/jcl3p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fjcl3p&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWJ1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=71f93ae4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/jcl3p</a><br />\n例如呢位香港母親嘅說話，可以加返字幕翻譯佢講緊乜嘢，加埋佢後續俾人開槍打嘅片<br />\n<br />\n又例如黑警發狂用胡椒水噴外籍人士塊面，都可以加返字幕解釋來龍去脈，話佢其實係行唔到；<br />\n同埋男教師被打到眼、男示威者被打到噴血、黑警阻住白車唔畀入、圍住地下示威者毆打呢啲片等等，<br />\n<br />\n相（例如黑警無理喺金鐘逗人）都可以寫返小小 Caption，解釋返件事係點<br />\n<br />\n總之希望可以動用到國際譴責黑警過份使用暴力，睇下政府係點樣壓迫平民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知諗唔諗得過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44184f96cd3c6d9205dc727400f47af55db615e","tid":1215235,"uid":212671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"依家最先頭可以係英文字幕，因為 NYT、BBC 已經有頭版報導<br />\n然後就係書面中文（台灣）、日文，呢兩個地方主要媒體都已經持續關注<br />\n之後無論係韓文、德文、法文，<br />\n全能嘅連登仔可以盡做，Send畀當地主流媒體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a99f5b7c40bab6fb8d09039daace51b46d2c606","tid":1215235,"uid":144833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"我都整咗個網頁擺各國語言<a href=\"https://noextraditiontochina.blogspot.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnoextraditiontochina.blogspot.com%2F&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWJ1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIo